            </tr>
        </table>

        <p>8) Provide any additional information that could be helpful to us in reaching a decision on your disability claim. If you need more space, please attach additional page(s).</p>

        <p>___________________________________________________________________________________________</p>
        <p>___________________________________________________________________________________________</p>
        <p>___________________________________________________________________________________________</p>
        <p>___________________________________________________________________________________________</p>

        <br><br><br><br>

        <p class="signature">
            <span>_________________________________________</span><span>__________________</span><span>________________________</span>
            <span>Name of person completing this form (Please print)</span><span>Date</span><span>Phone</span>
